            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><ex>A</ex><abbr>elia</abbr></expan> Valent&amp;lt;i=L&amp;gt;na <lb n="2"/>memor<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>an</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> posuit <lb n="3"/>fili<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> suis <expan><ex>A</ex><abbr>elio</abbr></expan> Vit<lb break="no" n="4"/>aliano et <expan><ex>A</ex><abbr>eli</abbr><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> Faus<lb break="no" n="5"/>tin<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XII <expan><ex>A</ex><abbr>elio</abbr></expan> Val<lb break="no" n="6"/>entiano <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> VIII <expan><abbr>Iulia</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Opta&amp;lt;t=C&amp;gt;ian<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> VIII <lb n="8"/>et <expan><ex>A</ex><abbr>elius</abbr></expan> Vitalianus <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XI 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fundjahr: in den 1980er Jahren. Z. 1-8: der letzte Buchstabe befindet sich jeweils auf dem Rahmen; Z. 9 auf dem unteren Rahmen. Zahlreiche Ligaturen; Z. 2: ANP-Ligatur über die Wortgrenze hinweg. Z. 8 (Anfang): TitAq 0520 (Autopsie): ET-Ligatur (A)elius; nach den Fotos in TitAq 0520 und lupa 10718 scheint ET-Ligatur (A)e&amp;lt;l&amp;gt;ius zu stehen. (B): AE 2010: Z. 8 (Anfang): et Iul(ius).</p>
            </div>
